{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "quality_and_reliability", "channel": "paint_defect_reduction", "user": "ethan_smith", "message": "Just a heads up everyone, we'll have a team meeting next Wednesday to discuss our overall progress. Please prepare your updates.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_innovation", "channel": "vehicle_compliance", "user": "john_doe", "message": "The new EV model passed all initial compliance tests. Good job team!", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "quality_and_reliability", "channel": "paint_defect_reduction", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "Ethan, do we have updates on the new paint drying equipment? The supplier was supposed to get back to us last week.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_innovation", "channel": "vehicle_compliance", "user": "ethan_smith", "message": "We're scheduled to attend the North American EV Compliance Conference next month. Please check your calendars.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "quality_and_reliability", "channel": "paint_defect_reduction", "user": "ethan_smith", "message": "Jane, I'm still waiting for the supplier's response. I'll follow-up with them again today.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_innovation", "channel": "vehicle_compliance", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Great news about the compliance tests. Let's ensure we maintain this standard in future models too.", "created_at": 1620505000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "quality_and_reliability", "channel": "paint_defect_reduction", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "Thanks, Ethan. We need those equipment updates to ensure our processes are running smoothly.", "created_at": 1620506000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "quality_and_reliability", "channel": "paint_defect_reduction", "user": "ethan_smith", "message": "Team, I'm happy to share some great news from our Q1 2025 report. We've made significant progress in reducing paint defects at our Austin, Texas facility.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "quality_and_reliability", "channel": "paint_defect_reduction", "user": "ethan_smith", "message": "After implementing the updated spray booth calibration protocol, we've seen a reduction in paint defects by 43%. This is a substantial improvement, and I want to thank everyone involved in the process.", "create_at": 1620500005000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "quality_and_reliability", "channel": "paint_defect_reduction", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "That's excellent news, Ethan! It's great to see the impact of our continuous efforts on improving the quality of our vehicles. Let's keep up the momentum.", "create_at": 1620500010000}}
